Package cn.nukkit.registry.mappings

Class ArrayMappingRegistry<M>

java.lang.Object
cn.nukkit.registry.mappings.MappingRegistry<M[]>
cn.nukkit.registry.mappings.ArrayMappingRegistry<M>
Type Parameters:
M - the mapping type
public class ArrayMappingRegistry<M> extends MappingRegistry<M[]>
An array registry that stores mappings as an array defined by ArrayMappingRegistry. The M represents the value that is to be stored as part of this array.
